---
title: Rustic Chicken Shepherd's Pie with Crispy Parmesan Topping & Pear Salad
description: When the temperature plummets, we often turn to homey, comforting classics to warm us from the inside out. If this sounds like the perfect cure to all your cold weather woes, look no further. Our recipe developers took the best parts of chicken pot pie and shepherd’s pie and combined them to create the world’s greatest dinner mash-up. Enjoy!

*Unfortunately, this
week’s mixed salad
leaves were in short
supply, so we’ve replaced
them with cos lettuce.
Don’t worry, the recipe
will be just as delicious,
just be sure to follow your
recipe card!*
